@Node "Introduction"

    This program patches rexxsyslib.library/ErrorMsg() function
    to localize ARexx error messages reading them from a catalog.

    RexxPatchError installs itself as a commodity, so you can
    Unable, Disable and Remove it from Exange.
@EndNode


@Node "Installation"

    To install RexxPatchError

    COPY:
    - RexxPatchError wherever you want (C: is the suggested drawer)
    - catalogs/YOUR_LANGUAGE/RexxPathError.catalog to Locale:catalogs/YOUR_LANGUAGE/
@EndNode


@Node "Requirements"

    RexxPatchError needs AmigaOS 2 or higher and of course ARexx installed.
@EndNode


