@Node "Usage"

    Not so much to say..

    Put somwhere in your startup-sequence or user-startup the command
    run >NIL: <NIL: RexxPatchError

    Controll it via Exange or run it again to quit it.

    A CTRL_C stops RexxPathError.
@EndNode


